VILLAGERS are too scared to go near this tree. They claim it is cursed. The tree, which has bits of cloths in different colours tied to it, is blamed for casting a dark cloud over Makahlule Village in Limpopo. The tree was discovered by Elvis Chauke and Magezi Khosa in the middle of the bush on Sunday afternoon. if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjsszj5W7pwpyLflmk4Kg9-gP2pZcY8wbDU9xnQwKtubAVi0HHZfPoq4mdjce4kaEpoBllfwGMvPST24n_pgutfBALznzFCEhYW5l6tX4Ya2ywPIxcGMp2rSZ0AVdHaVFhfhHg5PsaUwQKr3fvD5YnhvRjVrTkHI3fQHenJPjVQnx-lGThguZLiJQKEcymmB55fY-ZvewVduiV0VNcvZjJxIxuIwz_Fo3YYpGm13NejVDsmjLcNZ7jAh1jbARZ_Bqy0B8gzJVl2s-n9yA-IWZtUe1IUYq7Zs\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzIiLO1PkNuYuEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
